<br>
If your guild is close to raiding ToV then you might want to hold on to the lodi shield but don't if it will not happen in the next 2 months or so.<br>
<br>
On RN, a lodi shield sells for more than a DW bp. I would try to work out a deal to gain some extra cash. If you solo predominatly then I would use that money to buy a better weapon or upgrade backslot to a high AC one with the white bear pelt cloak for raiding.<br>
